### Welcome to BigOz on GitHub
All of my projects are listed, starting with the most recent.

[What's for Dinner?](http://bigoz.github.io/whats-for-dinner)
Utilizes computer vision and machine learning to process an image of ingredients and return a recipe that can be made using those ingredients.
